name: The Negligent human
description: The condition of the earth which is currently global warming because greedy human actions. They dredge the land, burn the forests, exploit minerals without limits. Nature's wrath! Fires, floods, earthquakes, and disease spread across the earth's surface. Greedy humans pretend to enjoy a luxurious life like corrupt rats who always eat away at the earth from outside and inside. Now nature is getting wrath! It all depends on what kind of human we want to be. If you want to be good, let's start with small thing and be close to the the nature.
